    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Commelina occulta.A, habit. B, lateral view of the spathaceous bract, showing cincinnus and peduncular structures. C, flower, frontal view. D, dissected flower. E, fruit. F. seed.A–F from D. Juárez-Gutierrez & G. Alatorre-de Alba 773. Drawing by A. Alvarez." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8308802/files/figure.png" ;
