<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8308812>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Floral variation in western Mexico Commelina (continued).A, C. leiocarpa. B, C. texcocana. C, C. standleyi. D, C. occulta. E, C. erecta. F, C. rufipes var. rufipes. Photos A, C–F by D. Juárez, B by D. Figueroa." ;
